1
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:18,208
- Nina: EVER SINCE THAT DAY,
THAT WONDERFUL DAY

2
00:00:18,291 --> 00:00:20,375
WHEN I FIRST MET
ZERO AND ICHII...

3
00:00:20,458 --> 00:00:21,583
- READY?
- YEAH.

4
00:00:21,666 --> 00:00:23,166
LET'S GET THIS THING STARTED.

5
00:00:23,250 --> 00:00:25,291
- ...THEY TOLD ME
THAT THEY WOULD PROTECT ME,

6
00:00:25,375 --> 00:00:29,791
I THOUGHT THAT THEY WOULD
ALWAYS BE HERE FOR ME.

7
00:00:29,875 --> 00:00:33,333
I THOUGHT
WE WOULD BE TOGETHER FOREVER.

8
00:00:33,416 --> 00:00:35,541
- WHAT'RE YOU GUYS DOING?

9
00:00:35,625 --> 00:00:38,750
- I NEVER REALIZED THAT THE TIME
WOULD ACTUALLY COME

10
00:00:38,833 --> 00:00:41,291
WHEN WE WOULD
HAVE TO SAY GOODBYE.

11
00:00:41,375 --> 00:00:44,458
BUT NOW
THAT TIME IS GETTING CLOSER.

12
00:00:44,541 --> 00:00:47,541
I WONDER WHAT ZERO AND ICHII
ARE PLANNING TO DO?

13
00:00:47,625 --> 00:00:50,541
ONCE THE CRYSTAL PEARL IS
REMOVED FROM MY BODY

14
00:00:50,625 --> 00:00:52,541
AND THE TEST ENDS,

15
00:00:52,625 --> 00:00:55,166
WHAT ARE THEY GONNA DO THEN?

16
00:01:00,875 --> 00:01:02,958
THE TEST IS ENDING SOON.

17
00:01:03,041 --> 00:01:06,916
IT'S ALMOST CHRISTMAS.

18
00:02:37,083 --> 00:02:39,583
WOW!
THIS ONE'S SO CUTE.

19
00:02:39,666 --> 00:02:41,333
- LOOKS TASTY.

20
00:02:41,416 --> 00:02:43,500
- IT HAS A LITTLE SANTA CLAUS
ON IT,

21
00:02:43,583 --> 00:02:46,083
AND REINDEERS TOO!

22
00:02:46,166 --> 00:02:48,541
- YEAH, I CAN'T WAIT
TO EAT SANTA CLAUS.

23
00:02:48,625 --> 00:02:51,541
- WAIT A MINUTE.
YOU CAN'T EAT SANTA.

24
00:02:51,625 --> 00:02:54,125
- WHAT?
BUT WHY CAN'T I, NINA?

25
00:02:54,208 --> 00:02:57,583
- 'CAUSE HE'S A CANDLE, SILLY.
HE WOULDN'T TASTE VERY GOOD.

26
00:02:57,666 --> 00:03:00,208
- IT'S ALMOST CHRISTMAS.
- THAT MEANS--

27
00:03:00,291 --> 00:03:03,958
- IT'S COMING UP SOON, ZERO.
- YEAH.

28
00:03:04,041 --> 00:03:06,250
TIME REALLY DOES FLY.

29
00:03:06,333 --> 00:03:08,458
I CAN'T BELIEVE
IT'S ALMOST CHRISTMAS.

30
00:03:08,541 --> 00:03:11,333
- YEAH IT IS.
SPEAKING OF,

31
00:03:11,416 --> 00:03:13,500
DO YOU TWO KNOW WHAT--
- HMM?

32
00:03:13,583 --> 00:03:16,625
OH!  NEVER MIND.
( laughs ) 

33
00:03:16,708 --> 00:03:19,125
- DON'T RUN OFF.
TELL US, NINA.

34
00:03:19,208 --> 00:03:21,166
- NO.

35
00:03:21,250 --> 00:03:23,291
IF I TOLD YOU,
IT WOULD RUIN THE SURPRISE.

36
00:03:23,375 --> 00:03:24,708
- WHATEVER!

37
00:03:24,791 --> 00:03:26,291
- ( thinking ) IT WOULDN'T BE
FUN IF I JUST ASKED THEM

38
00:03:26,375 --> 00:03:30,250
WHAT THEY WANTED FOR CHRISTMAS.
I HAVE TO FIGURE IT OUT MYSELF.

39
00:03:30,333 --> 00:03:34,416
I HAVE TO GET SOMETHING REALLY
SPECIAL FOR ZERO AND ICHII.

40
00:03:34,500 --> 00:03:37,000
- EH?

41
00:03:38,125 --> 00:03:39,708
AH!

42
00:03:39,791 --> 00:03:41,916
- AHHH!

43
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:45,625
OF COURSE I'LL HAVE TO GET
SOMETHING NICE FOR ZURA AS WELL.

44
00:03:45,708 --> 00:03:49,416
BECAUSE THEY'RE ALL
VERY IMPORTANT TO ME.

45
00:03:49,500 --> 00:03:52,208
THEY'LL ALWAYS BE MY FRIENDS.

46
00:03:57,125 --> 00:03:59,250
I WISH--

47
00:03:59,333 --> 00:04:03,875
I WISH THAT THIS HAPPINESS
COULD LAST FOREVER, 

48
00:04:03,958 --> 00:04:07,625
BUT THE SORCERY TEST
IS ALMOST OVER.

49
00:04:07,708 --> 00:04:09,583
IT'S CHRISTMASTIME.

50
00:04:15,083 --> 00:04:17,708
JEEZ!
I DON'T KNOW WHAT TO DO.

51
00:04:17,791 --> 00:04:19,833
WHAT SHOULD I GET THE GUYS?

52
00:04:19,916 --> 00:04:23,208
CLOTHES?
JEWELRY?

53
00:04:23,291 --> 00:04:26,166
I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT KIND OF GIFTS THEY LIKE.

54
00:04:26,250 --> 00:04:29,166
I GUESS HATS AREN'T REALLY
THAT TRENDY ANYMORE.

55
00:04:29,250 --> 00:04:31,833
AND I DON'T HAVE TIME
TO KNIT A SCARF FOR THEM.

56
00:04:31,916 --> 00:04:35,458
MAYBE I SHOULD JUST GET ICHII
A FANCY WALLET OR SOMETHING.

57
00:04:35,541 --> 00:04:38,916
AND ZERO, UM,
AN ORANGE VEST?

58
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,958
( moans )

59
00:04:41,041 --> 00:04:42,916
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

60
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,916
WHY ARE YOU STARING AT ME
LIKE THAT?

61
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,625
DID I DO SOMETHING WRONG?

62
00:04:46,708 --> 00:04:48,958
- NINA!
MAKE UP YOUR MIND.

63
00:04:49,041 --> 00:04:51,833
- 'CAUSE CHRISTMAS EVE IS
QUICKLY APPROACHING, YOU KNOW?

64
00:04:51,916 --> 00:04:54,208
- SO WHAT?
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN, "SO WHAT"?

65
00:04:54,291 --> 00:04:56,541
YOU KNOW WHAT CHRISTMAS EVE
IS ALL ABOUT, RIGHT?

66
00:04:56,625 --> 00:04:58,458
- NO.
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

67
00:04:58,541 --> 00:05:00,625
- YOU NEED TO DECIDE
WHAT YOU'RE GOING TO DO, NINA.

68
00:05:00,708 --> 00:05:02,625
- WELL,
I DON'T REALLY KNOW YET.

69
00:05:02,708 --> 00:05:06,583
- WE ARE TALKING ABOUT CHRISTMAS
EVE, DECEMBER 24th, THE BIG DAY.

70
00:05:06,666 --> 00:05:09,291
- BECAUSE THAT'S THE DAY

71
00:05:09,375 --> 00:05:11,875
YOU SPEND WITH THE PERSON
THAT YOU LOVE THE MOST.

72
00:05:11,958 --> 00:05:15,125
- AND IT ONLY COMES AROUND
ONCE A YEAR.

73
00:05:15,208 --> 00:05:18,208
- SO WHO ARE YOU GOING
TO SPEND THE DAY WITH, NINA?

74
00:05:18,291 --> 00:05:20,833
WITH ZERO
OR WITH ICHII?

75
00:05:20,916 --> 00:05:23,458
WHICH ONE?
COME ON, TELL US!

76
00:05:23,541 --> 00:05:26,125
WHICH ONE?
- AHHH!

77
00:05:26,208 --> 00:05:29,041
- WHO ARE YOU GOING TO SPEND
CHRISTMAS EVE WITH? HUH?

78
00:05:29,125 --> 00:05:31,625
- ( thinking ) "WHICH ONE"?

79
00:05:38,958 --> 00:05:42,541
- NINA.
SO YOU'VE CHOSEN ME.

80
00:05:42,625 --> 00:05:45,958
NINA.
NINA, MY LOVE!

81
00:05:46,041 --> 00:05:48,458
- HOLD IT RIGHT THERE.

82
00:05:48,541 --> 00:05:51,000
I WON'T LET YOU HAVE NINA!

83
00:05:51,083 --> 00:05:53,208
- OH YEAH?

84
00:05:53,291 --> 00:05:55,583
I LOVE NINA MORE THAN ANYONE
IN THE WORLD.

85
00:05:55,666 --> 00:05:57,250
AND I WON'T LET HER GO.
- HUH?

86
00:05:57,333 --> 00:05:59,500
- FIGHT ME FOR HER.
- AS YOU WISH.

87
00:05:59,583 --> 00:06:02,750
- ( both grunting )

88
00:06:04,291 --> 00:06:06,166
- STOP IT!  STOP IT!

89
00:06:06,250 --> 00:06:09,125
THIS IS MY FAULT.
PLEASE STOP FIGHTING.

90
00:06:09,208 --> 00:06:12,791
I CAN'T CHOOSE.
I CAN'T CHOOSE BETWEEN YOU.

91
00:06:12,875 --> 00:06:15,916
I JUST CAN'T DO IT.  AHH!

92
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:20,291
PLEASE STOP IT ALREADY.
STOP!

93
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,750
I CAN'T TAKE ANY MORE OF THIS.

94
00:06:23,833 --> 00:06:25,666
PLEASE STOP FIGHTING.
- HUH?

95
00:06:25,750 --> 00:06:27,750
- WHAT IN THE WORLD
ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

96
00:06:27,833 --> 00:06:31,833
- HUH? UH, UH...
( laughing )

97
00:06:31,916 --> 00:06:35,458
OH NOTHING,
FORGET ABOUT IT.

98
00:06:35,541 --> 00:06:39,333
 ( thinking ) THERE'S NO WAY
I CAN PICK JUST ONE.

99
00:06:39,416 --> 00:06:42,375
I WANT TO SPEND CHRISTMAS EVE
WITH ALL OF 'EM .

100
00:06:42,458 --> 00:06:46,708
- ( grunting )
- EVEN ZURA.

101
00:06:46,791 --> 00:06:48,916
- THIS ISN'T THE WAY
TO THE CAKE SHOP.

102
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:52,291
I WANT CAKE.
- UH, NINA?

103
00:06:52,375 --> 00:06:54,708
- JUST WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

104
00:06:54,791 --> 00:06:58,000
- JUST GIVE ME
SOME TIME TO THINK, OKAY?

105
00:06:58,083 --> 00:07:00,666
- WHAT'S WITH HER?
SHE'S ACTING STRANGELY.

106
00:07:00,750 --> 00:07:03,583
- NEVER TRY
TO UNDERSTAND A WOMAN, ZURA.

107
00:07:03,666 --> 00:07:05,333
- COME ON.

108
00:07:05,416 --> 00:07:06,625
- ( thinking ) THIS IS
OKAY, ISN'T IT?

109
00:07:06,708 --> 00:07:08,500
I DON'T HAVE TO
PICK BETWEEN THEM.

110
00:07:08,583 --> 00:07:11,875
I JUST WANT TO BE WITH EVERYONE
NOW-- ZERO, ICHII, AND ZURA.

111
00:07:11,958 --> 00:07:13,291
- HEY, NINA,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

112
00:07:13,375 --> 00:07:14,708
- YEAH, WHAT'S GOING ON?

113
00:07:14,791 --> 00:07:18,541
- ( thinking ) I WANT TO
SPEND CHRISTMAS WITH EVERYBODY.

114
00:07:18,625 --> 00:07:22,333
OH!  I STILL DON'T KNOW
WHAT I'M GONNA DO.

115
00:07:22,416 --> 00:07:25,291
I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT TO GET THOSE TWO GUYS.

116
00:07:25,375 --> 00:07:27,583
WHY DOES THIS HAVE TO BE
SO DIFFICULT?

117
00:07:27,666 --> 00:07:29,625
I MEAN, WHAT IN THE WORLD
DO YOU GET A SORCERER

118
00:07:29,708 --> 00:07:31,375
FOR CHRISTMAS ANYWAY?

119
00:07:31,458 --> 00:07:34,458
AH!  THAT'S PERFECT.
I'VE GOT IT.

120
00:07:34,541 --> 00:07:37,708
MERRY CHRISTMAS!
( laughing ) 

121
00:07:37,791 --> 00:07:41,916
AND YOUR SPECIAL PRESENT
IS ME, NINA!

122
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:45,333
NAH. I'D BETTER COME UP WITH
SOMETHING A LITTLE BETTER

123
00:07:45,416 --> 00:07:46,791
TO GET THOSE GUYS.

124
00:07:46,875 --> 00:07:49,833
WELL, I GUESS I COULD
JUST CASUALLY ASK THEM

125
00:07:49,916 --> 00:07:51,250
WHAT THEY MIGHT LIKE.

126
00:07:51,333 --> 00:07:54,333
THERE'S NO HARM IN THAT.
I WONDER IF THEY'RE STILL AWAKE.

127
00:07:54,416 --> 00:07:56,458
I SURE HOPE SO.

128
00:07:56,541 --> 00:07:58,916
- SO WHAT DO YOU THINK
WE SHOULD DO?

129
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:02,375
- DO YOU MEAN
ABOUT CHRISTMAS?

130
00:08:02,458 --> 00:08:05,708
- YEAH. I THINK WE SHOULD
GET HER A PARTING GIFT

131
00:08:05,791 --> 00:08:08,208
BECAUSE WE'RE LEAVING.

132
00:08:11,041 --> 00:08:13,125
- I SUPPOSE.

133
00:08:13,208 --> 00:08:17,875
AFTER THE TEST IS OVER
ON CHRISTMAS, WE'LL LEAVE.

134
00:08:17,958 --> 00:08:20,291
- RIGHT.
WE WON'T HAVE TO STAY

135
00:08:20,375 --> 00:08:22,875
AND PROTECT NINA
AND THE PEARL ANY LONGER.

136
00:08:22,958 --> 00:08:25,208
- AND THEN WE GET
TO GO BACK HOME.

137
00:08:25,291 --> 00:08:28,916
AND NINA WILL BE
LEFT ALL ALONE.

138
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:32,500
- YEAH.
OUR TIME HERE'S JUST ABOUT UP.

139
00:08:32,583 --> 00:08:35,125
BUT BEFORE WE LEAVE,
WE SHOULD DEFINITELY

140
00:08:35,208 --> 00:08:37,583
GET A REALLY SPECIAL PRESENT
FOR NINA.

141
00:08:37,666 --> 00:08:40,208
SOMETHING...

142
00:08:40,291 --> 00:08:44,708
- ( thinking ) WHAT?
A PARTING GIFT?

143
00:08:44,791 --> 00:08:49,000
I GUESS
THEY'RE REALLY LEAVING.

144
00:08:49,083 --> 00:08:52,833
EVER SINCE THAT DAY,
WHEN I FIRST MET ZERO AND ICHII

145
00:08:52,916 --> 00:08:55,458
AND THEY TOLD ME
THAT THEY WOULD PROTECT ME,

146
00:08:55,541 --> 00:08:57,875
I NEVER REALIZED
THAT THE TIME WOULD COME

147
00:08:57,958 --> 00:09:01,833
WHEN WE WOULD HAVE TO
SAY GOODBYE.

148
00:09:01,916 --> 00:09:03,583
- DEFENSE MAGIC!

149
00:09:05,208 --> 00:09:07,791
- I GUESS
THEY'LL HAVE TO GO BACK HOME

150
00:09:07,875 --> 00:09:10,250
ONCE THE EXAM IS OVER.

151
00:09:10,333 --> 00:09:14,000
AND WHETHER THEY PASS IT OR NOT,
I'LL NEVER SEE THEM AGAIN.

152
00:09:14,083 --> 00:09:16,625
AND THEY'LL GO BACK
TO THE MAGIC WORLD,

153
00:09:16,708 --> 00:09:20,416
LEAVING NOTHING BUT THAT
LOLLIPOP TO REMEMBER THEM BY.

154
00:09:20,500 --> 00:09:23,041
( sobbing )

155
00:09:23,125 --> 00:09:26,125
I WISH
THERE WERE NO SORCERY TEST.

156
00:09:26,208 --> 00:09:29,250
I WISH THERE WERE NO CHRISTMAS.

157
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:34,583
OUR TIME TOGETHER
IS ABOUT TO END.

158
00:09:34,666 --> 00:09:36,541
THE TEST IS ALMOST OVER.

159
00:09:36,625 --> 00:09:39,291
AND IT'S ALMOST CHRISTMAS.

160
00:09:39,375 --> 00:09:40,916
- Female voice: NINA.

161
00:09:52,625 --> 00:09:55,500
- ( bell tolling )

162
00:09:55,583 --> 00:09:58,208
- JEEZ, THAT STUDENT COUNCIL
MEETING TOOK FOREVER.

163
00:09:58,291 --> 00:10:00,333
I'M RUNNING SO LATE NOW.

164
00:10:00,416 --> 00:10:02,708
UH, NOBODY'S HERE.

165
00:10:02,791 --> 00:10:06,291
I GUESS ZERO AND ICHII
HAVE GONE HOME ALREADY.

166
00:10:06,375 --> 00:10:09,500
THAT'S PRETTY RUDE OF THEM
TO LEAVE WITHOUT ME.

167
00:10:09,583 --> 00:10:12,791
NO BIG DEAL. I CAN ALWAYS
WALK HOME BY MYSELF.

168
00:10:12,875 --> 00:10:16,958
I'LL BE JUST FINE WITHOUT THOSE
TWO PROTECTING ME. HA!

169
00:10:17,041 --> 00:10:19,416
 ( thinking )
BUT NOW THAT I THINK ABOUT IT,

170
00:10:19,500 --> 00:10:22,291
I HAVEN'T BEEN ALONE
IN A WHILE.

171
00:10:22,375 --> 00:10:25,291
ZERO AND ICHII
HAVE BEEN WITH ME ALL THE TIME.

172
00:10:25,375 --> 00:10:28,625
SO I HAVEN'T EVEN HAD A CHANCE
TO BE ALONE.

173
00:10:28,708 --> 00:10:31,500
BUT I GUESS I'LL HAVE PLENTY
OF TIME TO BE BY MYSELF

174
00:10:31,583 --> 00:10:33,125
AFTER CHRISTMAS.

175
00:10:33,208 --> 00:10:36,375
I MIGHT AS WELL
GET USED TO IT NOW.

176
00:10:36,458 --> 00:10:38,958
I NEED TO BE COMFORTABLE
BEING BY MYSELF AGAIN.

177
00:10:39,041 --> 00:10:40,958
- Ichii: NINA.

178
00:10:41,041 --> 00:10:43,583
THERE YOU ARE.
HOW DID YOUR MEETING GO?

179
00:10:43,666 --> 00:10:47,458
- WELL, IT SURE TOOK FOREVER.
I THOUGHT IT'D NEVER END.

180
00:10:47,541 --> 00:10:49,750
- NOW CAN WE GO BACK
TO THE CAKE SHOP, NINA?

181
00:10:49,833 --> 00:10:52,125
'CAUSE I'M GETTING
REALLY HUNGRY, YOU KNOW.

182
00:10:52,208 --> 00:10:54,875
- ZERO, ICHII?
- ( all laugh )

183
00:10:54,958 --> 00:10:56,916
YOU TWO WAITED FOR ME?

184
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:59,458
BUT-- BUT--

185
00:10:59,541 --> 00:11:03,541
HOW AM I SUPPOSED TO PRETEND
THAT EVERYTHING'S ALL RIGHT,

186
00:11:03,625 --> 00:11:06,500
THAT THEY'RE NOT
ABOUT TO LEAVE ME?

187
00:11:06,583 --> 00:11:09,291
( crying )
- HEY, NINA!

188
00:11:09,375 --> 00:11:11,416
WAIT!

189
00:11:11,500 --> 00:11:12,875
- I'M SORRY.

190
00:11:12,958 --> 00:11:14,791
I CAN'T GO
TO THE CAKE SHOP TODAY.

191
00:11:14,875 --> 00:11:17,958
BECAUSE I'M LATE
FOR AN APPOINTMENT

192
00:11:18,041 --> 00:11:20,458
WITH HATSUKA AND YOUKA.

193
00:11:20,541 --> 00:11:24,083
- Ichii: NINA, WAIT.
- NINA!

194
00:11:24,166 --> 00:11:27,291
- LET'S GO.
WE STILL HAVE TO PROTECT HER.

195
00:11:27,375 --> 00:11:29,875
- RIGHT.
- COME ON.

196
00:11:29,958 --> 00:11:33,541
- Hatsuka:
HEY, NINA, OVER HERE.

197
00:11:33,625 --> 00:11:36,666
- HEY, SORRY I'M LATE.
WHAT'S GOIN' ON?

198
00:11:36,750 --> 00:11:39,666
- BUT WHERE'S ZERO AND ICHII?

199
00:11:39,750 --> 00:11:41,416
- I DON'T KNOW.

200
00:11:41,500 --> 00:11:43,958
- WHAT?
BUT WHY AREN'T YOU WITH THEM?

201
00:11:44,041 --> 00:11:46,583
- I DON'T HAVE TO
BE WITH THEM ALL THE TIME.

202
00:11:46,666 --> 00:11:49,458
- WHAT?
YOU'RE ALWAYS WITH THEM.

203
00:11:49,541 --> 00:11:52,291
- I JUST WANT
TO HAVE A LITTLE CAKE.

204
00:11:52,375 --> 00:11:55,250
- DID YOU GUYS HAVE A FIGHT?
- NOT REALLY.

205
00:11:55,333 --> 00:11:59,625
- Both: UM, SO WHAT DO YOU THINK
IS GOING ON?

206
00:11:59,708 --> 00:12:02,041
- LET'S SEE...
- Zero: I THOUGHT SHE SAID

207
00:12:02,125 --> 00:12:04,083
SHE DIDN'T WANT TO COME
TO THE CAKE SHOP TODAY.

208
00:12:04,166 --> 00:12:06,791
- IT'S NOT FAIR.
SHE'S EATING WITHOUT ME.

209
00:12:06,875 --> 00:12:08,833
- YEAH, WE SHOULD GO JOIN HER.

210
00:12:08,916 --> 00:12:13,541
HEY, WHAT ARE YOU DOING, ICHII?
WHY CAN'T I GO AND JOIN NINA?

211
00:12:13,625 --> 00:12:15,750
- JUST LEAVE HER ALONE.
- BUT WHY?

212
00:12:15,833 --> 00:12:18,791
- 'CAUSE SHE MAY NOT
WANT TO DO THIS ANYMORE, ZERO.

213
00:12:18,875 --> 00:12:21,500
- WHAT?
NO WAY.  SHE'S FINE.

214
00:12:21,583 --> 00:12:25,291
- JUST THINK ABOUT IT.
SHE'S PROBABLY SICK OF US.

215
00:12:25,375 --> 00:12:27,791
- BUT, ICHII,
WHAT MAKES YOU SAY THAT?

216
00:12:27,875 --> 00:12:30,750
- LET GO. WE HAVE TO
PROTECT THE CRYSTAL PEARL.

217
00:12:30,833 --> 00:12:34,000
WE HAVE TO.
WE DON'T HAVE A CHOICE HERE.

218
00:12:34,083 --> 00:12:36,250
- BUT IT JUST SEEMS
LIKE A SELFISH REASON

219
00:12:36,333 --> 00:12:38,083
FOR US TO DO THIS TO HER.

220
00:12:38,166 --> 00:12:39,708
- ( all laughing )

221
00:12:39,791 --> 00:12:41,750
- NINA IS JUST
AN ORDINARY HUMAN GIRL.

222
00:12:41,833 --> 00:12:44,166
NEITHER THE CRYSTAL PEARL
NOR THE SORCERY TEST

223
