- YOU HAVE TO DECIDE
FOR YOURSELF.

312
00:16:35,375 --> 00:16:37,666
SO WHAT ARE YOU GOING TO DO?

313
00:16:37,750 --> 00:16:40,125
YOU HAVE TO MAKE UP YOUR MIND.

314
00:16:40,208 --> 00:16:42,250
NINA?

315
00:16:42,333 --> 00:16:43,458
- I WANT--

316
00:16:44,875 --> 00:16:48,250
- San: HEY, CHECK IT OUT!
NINA!

317
00:16:48,333 --> 00:16:50,333
ISN'T IT GREAT?

