IF YOU COULD PRETEND

352
00:18:27,541 --> 00:18:29,541
THAT YOU DON'T KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT IT.

353
00:18:29,625 --> 00:18:32,166
- OH!
THIS DRAWING IS MY MASTERPIECE.

354
00:18:32,250 --> 00:18:33,416
- Nina: SHE'S REALLY EXCITED.

355
00:18:33,500 --> 00:18:34,791
- I CAN'T WAIT FOR THE SORCERY
TEST TO BE OVER

356
00:18:34,875 --> 00:18:36,458
AND FOR CHRISTMASTIME
TO BE HERE ALREADY.

357
00:18:36,541 --> 00:18:39,083
- EVEN ROKKA'S GETTING READY
TO GIVE A GIFT

358
00:18:39,166 --> 00:18:41,208
TO THE PERSON SHE CARES ABOUT,

359
00:18:41,291 --> 00:18:44,291
BECAUSE SHE WANTS TO TELL
THAT PERSON HOW SHE FEELS,

360
00:18:44,375 --> 00:18:48,041
BECAUSE SHE WANTS TO EXPRESS
HER APPRECIATION TO THAT PERSON.

361
00:18:48,125 --> 00:18:51,666
ZERO AND ICHII HAVE BROUGHT
SO MUCH INTO MY LIFE,

362
00:18:51,750 --> 00:18:53,625
MORE THAN THEY'LL EVER KNOW.

363
00:18:53,708 --> 00:18:55,791
