366
00:19:01,583 --> 00:19:03,083
- I GOT YOU.

367
00:19:03,166 --> 00:19:05,208
- Nina: WE SHARE A MUCH STRONGER
CONNECTION,

368
00:19:05,291 --> 00:19:08,083
