370
00:19:14,166 --> 00:19:16,750
I'VE THOUGHT EVERYTHING OVER.

371
00:19:16,833 --> 00:19:19,958
AND EVEN THOUGH I DON'T KNOW
ANYTHING ABOUT THEIR PAST,

372
00:19:20,041 --> 00:19:22,000
I KNOW I CAN TRUST THEM BOTH

373
00:19:22,083 --> 00:19:24,708
AND THAT THEY'LL PROTECT ME,
BECAUSE THEY GAVE THEIR WORD

374
00:19:24,791 --> 00:19:26,708
AND THAT'S ALL I NEED.

375
00:19:26,791 --> 00:19:28,708
SO I REALLY
APPRECIATE THE OFFER,

376
00:19:28,791 --> 00:19:30,708
BUT I'M GONNA HAVE TO STAY
WITH ZERO AND ICHII.

377
00:19:30,791 --> 00:19:34,250
