399
00:20:35,250 --> 00:20:38,083
WILL BE ERASED FOREVER--
ALL GONE.

400
00:20:38,166 --> 00:20:40,166
AND IF IT WOULD
MAKE YOU FEEL BETTER,

401
00:20:40,250 --> 00:20:42,208
THEN I WOULDN'T MIND
DOING IT FOR YOU,

402
00:20:42,291 --> 00:20:44,208
BUT IT'S UP TO YOU.
