403
00:20:44,291 --> 00:20:46,708
- YOU HAVE TO DECIDE
FOR YOURSELF.

404
00:20:46,791 --> 00:20:49,041
SO WHAT ARE YOU GOING TO DO?

405
00:20:49,125 --> 00:20:52,916
YOU HAVE TO MAKE UP YOUR MIND.
NINA?

406
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:56,250
- I WANT YOU

407
00:20:56,333 --> 00:20:59,041
TO ERASE ALL OF MY MEMORIES,

408
00:20:59,125 --> 00:21:03,083
BECAUSE IT'S-- IT'S TOO PAINFUL
TO BE WITHOUT ZERO AND ICHII.

409
00:21:03,166 --> 00:21:06,208
