00:22:38,375 --> 00:22:40,500
EVEN AFTER YOU GO BACK
TO THE MAGIC WORLD,

445
00:22:40,583 --> 00:22:42,916
DON'T FORGET ABOUT ME.
- NINA.

446
00:22:43,000 --> 00:22:46,625
- AND YOU-- YOU TWO
WILL BE MY PRINCES FOREVER.

447
00:22:46,708 --> 00:22:48,916
- NINA.

448
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:52,083
- ( thinking ) ZERO, ICHII--

449
00:22:52,166 --> 00:22:54,541
I NEVER WANT
TO BE APART FROM THEM.

450
00:22:54,625 --> 00:22:57,208
BUT THE TEST IS ABOUT TO END

451
00:22:57,291 --> 00:23:00,458
AND THERE'S NOTHING
I CAN DO ABOUT IT.

452
00:23:00,541 --> 00:23:03,166
CHRISTMASTIME
IS GETTING CLOSER.

453
00:23:03,250 --> 00:23:06,791
