00:23:06,875 --> 00:23:10,166
BUT I WANT TO BELIEVE THAT WE
DON'T HAVE TO BE APART FOREVER.

455
00:23:10,250 --> 00:23:14,166
AND THAT ONE DAY,
WHEN I LEAST EXPECT IT,

456
00:23:14,250 --> 00:23:16,250
I'LL SEE THEM AGAIN.

457
00:23:16,333 --> 00:23:21,500
ZERO, ICHII,
THANK YOU.

458
00:23:21,583 --> 00:23:24,833
THANK YOU
FOR SO MANY MEMORIES.

459
00:23:29,375 --> 00:23:30,958
- HUH?
- ( grunts )

460
00:23:31,041 --> 00:23:35,291
- Zero: WHO ARE YOU?
- MY NAME IS RIRU.

461
00:23:35,375 --> 00:23:37,833
I'M HERE TO HELP NINA.

462
00:25:17,250 --> 00:25:19,583
Riru:
NOW TAKE THIS MEDICINE.

463
00:25:19,666 --> 00:25:22,833
IF YOU DO, THE CRYSTAL PEARL
WILL LEAVE YOUR BODY.

464
00:25:22,916 --> 00:25:25,958
- Zero: YOU DON'T HAVE TO, NINA.
WE'LL PROTECT YOU.

465
00:25:26,041 --> 00:25:28,333
- Bird: STOP THAT NONSENSE.
IT'S DANGEROUS!

466
00:25:28,416 --> 00:25:30,500
IT COULD BE LIFE THREATENING!

467
00:25:30,583 --> 00:25:32,375
- BUT WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO DO?

468
00:25:32,458 --> 00:25:35,958
I DON'T WANT TO BE APART
FROM ZERO AND ICHII.

469
00:25:36,041 --> 00:25:38,375
NEXT TIME
ON "SAVE ME! LOLLIPOP"...

470
00:25:40,916 --> 00:25:44,375
- YOU'LL TAKE IT BECAUSE THAT'S
THE ANSWER YOU'VE CHOSEN.

